## 🚀 Running Aurora

### Prerequisites
- Node.js (v16+)
- AngehLang runtime environment
- Photonic substrate (simulated if hardware unavailable)

### Launch Commands
```bash
# Interactive Aurora interface
node aurora_interface.js

# Direct AngehLang execution
node --loader ./runtime-loader.js aurora_runner.angeh

# IDE integration
node improved-ide-server.js
# Then visit: http://localhost:8080
```

### Available Commands
- `status` - System diagnostics
- `personality` - Personality matrix
- `help` - Command reference
- `bye` - Graceful shutdown

